"<action>Show animations of your own moves as they occur.</action> This is an "
"aid for beginners, because it slows down the animations. Experienced players "
"can turn this option off and moves are then animated at high speed, taking "
"about a tenth of a second to turn 90 degrees."
msgstr ""
"Mostrar as animacións dos teus movementos cando se producen. Isto axuda os "
"principiantes porque enlentece as animacións. Os xogadores experimentados "
"poden apagar esta opción e así os movementos anímanse a alta velocidade, co "
"que leva unha décima de segundo xirar 90 graos."

